==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Ancient Greek]] [[κίνησις]] (''kinesis'') "motion, movememt", from [[κινέω]] (''kineo'') "to move, to put in motion".
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''kinesis'''
# the [[movement]] of an [[organism]] in [[response]] to an [[external]] [[stimulus]]
